item.title: Help, Old timer coder
item.dc:creator: @danknightxx danknightxx
item.description:
@danknightxx wrote:

[quote=“I Vain I”]Project Insanity handles item definitions through if statements, and switch statements.

So, it could be:

if (i == ####) { //append definitions to the following if-statement
    /*
    definitions go here
    */
} //close definitions

Or

case ####: //append definitions to the following case of the switch-statement /* definitions go here */ break; //close definitions [/quote]

oh right

so brake; is }

meh ok ty
